{"tid":2090498,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中美媒體戰升級  華索四駐京美媒營運資料","createTime":"2020-07-02T07:58:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T07:58:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d949fa15bea3aab3537790e2ccab5602e38eca7e","tid":2090498,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T07:58:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200702/VXZXHJRR6SXPG6TPRNOT6KLOHU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200702%2FVXZXHJRR6SXPG6TPRNOT6KLOHU%2F&d=oBn6KkEvnt0QU92xe9ZG8BlCv%2FutJLQSKuuf3SGwDjg%3D&h=d40cf873\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200702%2FVXZXHJRR6SXPG6TPRNOT6KLOHU%2F&h=53eb13d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200702/VXZXHJRR6SXPG6TPRNOT6KLOHU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n中美媒體戰升級 <br />\n華索四駐京美媒營運資料<br />\n<br />\n中美媒體戰自年初起持續升級。美國先後宣佈將新華社、央視等多間中國官媒列為「外國使團」，中國外交部昨宣佈反制措施，要求美聯社、美國哥倫比亞廣播公司等四間美國駐京傳媒，要七天內向中方申報詳細資料、財務運作情況。《環球時報》總編輯胡錫進昨引用港區國安法條文，指駐港國安公署職責包括加強在港外媒的管理，暗示中美媒體戰可針對在港外媒。<br />\n<br />\n美國2月將新華社等五間中國媒體駐美機構列為「外國使團」，6月更將範圍擴大到央視等四間媒體。外交部發言人趙立堅昨在記者會上宣佈，近年美國政府對中國駐美傳媒機構的正常報道活動「無端設限、無理刁難」，對中國媒體的歧視和政治打壓不斷升級，中方就此針對美媒採取反制措施。最新接受規管的是美聯社（AP）、國際合眾社（UPI）、哥倫比亞廣播公司（CBS）、全國公共廣播電台（NPR）。它們須在指定時間內，向中國申報在華所有職員、財務、所持有的不動產等書面資料。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/pLxcRfBGABayiDq0EPVXTP4N5kA=/190x127/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UR4EP2XFR7F4QIPNOR7N5X34TY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FpLxcRfBGABayiDq0EPVXTP4N5kA%3D%2F190x127%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUR4EP2XFR7F4QIPNOR7N5X34TY.jpg&h=33b82225&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n外媒在華採訪阻力重重，在中美角力持續下料越趨艱難。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Mj1wT7TfEIdDuTup7lwLrZyFx9w=/489x303/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IWSLACCVIK2SXN3CCAVCEP6HRM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMj1wT7TfEIdDuTup7lwLrZyFx9w%3D%2F489x303%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIWSLACCVIK2SXN3CCAVCEP6HRM.gif&h=ce8853d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中央要求官媒「姓黨」，報道要體現黨的意志。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/w8m0KmYdeCbKfSvKFxhxy5XR-iY=/489x303/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/43OSNX6NNIKTH7YT7ZFO56QPMQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fw8m0KmYdeCbKfSvKFxhxy5XR-iY%3D%2F489x303%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F43OSNX6NNIKTH7YT7ZFO56QPMQ.gif&h=0413716c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國早前將駐美新華社列為「外國使團」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n胡錫進暗示可報復港外媒<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：涉走私彈藥被拘 聯邦快遞機師獲釋<br />\n<br />\n趙立堅稱，<br />\n...................................<br />\n，暴露其自我標榜的「新聞自由」的虛偽性。<br />\n<br />\n胡錫進昨表示，<br />\n...........................<br />\n較美方對中國的施壓點更多」。<br />\n<br />\n中美這場媒體戰的源頭，<br />\n...................................<br />\n並指四間媒體是中共宣傳機器。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n分柝指驅逐戰美損失大<br />\n<br />\n外媒分析指<br />\n......................<br />\n華盛頓難以獲勝。<br />\n<br />\n浸會大學新聞系專業應用副教授李文則感嘆，<br />\n.........................<br />\n將影響世界了解中國情況。<br />\n<br />\n外交部/《蘋果》記者"}]}